<script type="text/javascript">
  if(location.pathname === '/'){
    var queryMap = {};
    var hashStr = location.hash;
    var queryStr = location.search;
    var generateQueryMap = function(str){
      str.replace(/\?|#/g, '').split('&').map(function (queryItem){
        queryItem = queryItem.split('=');
        queryMap[queryItem[0]] = queryItem[1];
      })
    };
    var getQueryValue = function(k){
      return queryMap[k]? queryMap[k]: '';
    };
    var leftpad = function(s, num, placeholder){
      s = String(s);
      while(s.length<num){
        s = placeholder+s;
      }
      return s;
    };
    if(queryStr){
      generateQueryMap(queryStr);
    }
    if(hashStr){
      generateQueryMap(hashStr);  // hash 优先级较高，如果出现和query中 key相同的会将query中的替换掉
    }
    var linkMap = {
      'showcinemas': '/cinema/movie/'+ getQueryValue('movieid') +'?_v_=yes',
      'showtime': '/shows/'+ getQueryValue('cinemaid') +'?_v_=yes&movieid='+ getQueryValue('movieid') +'&date='+ getQueryValue('date'),
      'seats': '/seats/'+ getQueryValue('showDate').replace(/-/g,'') + leftpad(getQueryValue('showId'), 7, '0') +'?_v_=yes',
      'buy': '/createOrder/'+ getQueryValue('id') +'?_v_=yes',
      'changecity': '/city?_v_=yes',
      'comment': '/replies/' + getQueryValue('id') + '?_v_=yes'
    };
    if(queryMap.tmp){
      location.href = linkMap[queryMap.tmp] || '/?_v_=yes'
    }
  }
</script>

<script>
    $(window).on('click', '[data-bid]', function(){
        var bid = $(this).data('bid');
        var lab = $(this).data('lab');
        if((typeof lab) !== 'object'){
          lab = eval('(' + lab + ')');
        }
        var data = {
          nm : 'mge',
          val_bid: bid,
          val_cid: window.cid,
          event_type: 'click'
        }
        if(lab){
          data.val_lab = lab;
        }
        Analytics('event', data);
    });
</script>
